root.description: Raydium Jito Sniper is a high-speed trading bot built for the Solana network that targets new or low-liquidity tokens listed on Raydium AMM. It leverages Jito Bundles to send transactions directly to Solana block leaders, bypassing the public mempool, which helps prevent front-running and ensures faster execution.
root.name: solana-raydium-jito-sniper
